(103009, 'Saurabh Singh Thakur', '../faculty/images/ssthakur_cse.jpg', 'Lecturer', 'Computer Science & Engineering', '<b>M.Tech </b>(Pursuing), IIT Kharagpur, Kharagpur, W.B., India\n<b>B.Tech</b>, Rajiv Gandhi Technical University, Bhopal, M.P., India\n\n<b>Saurabh Singh</b> joined the Institute in February 2011\n                                                                        ', 'B-20, NIT Campus, Jamshedpur - 831014                                                                                         ', '+91-657- 2372900', '+91-8797022904', 'saurabh.cse@nitjsr.ac.in', '<p><b>Professional Synopsis</b></p><ul><li>Young, energetic and result oriented professional with 03 years of experience in Teaching as Lecturer with strong academic background.</li><li>Exceptional communication, analytical, inter personal and problem solving skills.</li><li>Ability to prioritize and remain focused on the essence of an issue</li><li>Skilled at learning new concepts quickly, working well under pressure and communicating ideas clearly and effectively</li><li>Outstanding within a fast-paced environment, continually taking on increased levels of responsibility</li></ul><p>&nbsp;<b>Vision</b></p><ul><li>To achieve academic excellence through rigor, relevance, improved performance and perseverance.</li></ul><p><b>Mission</b></p><ul><li>To train and transform young minds into positive, motivated &amp; thinking technologist, who are highly enthusiastic to explore new possibilities in the field of science &amp; technology for the betterment of the society.</li></ul><p><b>Technical Proficiency</b></p><ul><li>Computer Networks</li><li>Data Structure</li><li>DBMS</li><li>Programming in C/C++</li><li>Computer Architecture</li><li>Operating Systems</li></ul><p><b>&nbsp;</b><b>Research Interest</b></p><ul><li>Networking</li><li>Image Processing</li></ul><p><b>Research Publications<br></b></p><ol><li>Rajesh Duvvuru<b>,</b>Sunil Kumar Singh, <b>Saurabh Singh Thakur</b>, S.B.L. Seksena. <b>