ute of Engineers</li><li>Life Fellow Member of Indian Geotechnical Society</li><li>Member of the International Society of Soil Mechanics and Foundation Engineering</li><li>Life Member of Indian Road Congress</li><li>Member of the National Board of Accreditation Committee</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p><b>Publications</b></p><p>Thirty nos. of technical research paper published in National/International Journals and Conferences in the field of Geotechnical Engineering, Concrete Technology, Environmental &nbsp;Engg. And Traffic &amp; Transportation Engg.</p>'),
