A. </em></b></p><p>Participated with a group of student in the<b><em> SASOL BAJA, 2010 at South Africa. </em></b>An competition to race all-terrain vehicles designed and fabricated by the team.</p><p><em>&nbsp;</em> Delivered an Invited Guest Lecture at the on <em>Thermodynamic Analysis of </em><em>Advanced Gas Turbine Based </em><em>Power Plant Cycles&nbsp; </em>on the 14<sup>th</sup> of October 2010 <em>at </em>the Mechanical and Aerospace Engg. Department,<em> University of Pretoria, South Africa.</em></p><p><em>&nbsp;</em></p><p><span class=\\"underline\\">&nbsp;<b>Ph.D Supervision:</b></span></p><p><b>&nbsp;<span class=\\"\\\\&quot;\\\\\\\\&quot;bold\\\\\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\">Supervised</span> TWO and </b>Supervising One Ph.D. scholars in the field of gas turbine based combined cycle power plants</p><p><b>&nbsp;</b></p><p><span class=\\"underline\\"><b>LABORATORIES DEVELOPED</b><b>:</b></span></p><ul><li>Retrofitting of Petrol and Diesel Engines in Internal Combustion Engine Lab.</li><li>Developing a 6-stroke conceptual C. I engine in association with CUMMINS</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span class=\\"underline\\"><b>Sponsored Research Project:</b></span></p><p>Working on a Technology Gap Analysis Study for auto-component cluster at Jamshedpur. The research project is sponsored by TIFAC&nbsp; New Delhi (Govt. of India).</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><b>SHORT-TERM COURSES ORGANIZED</b><b>: </b></p><p>Coordinator for an ISTE sponsored Teacher Induction Training Programme 3-week Short Term Course on Teacher\\''s Role in Engineering Education- 25<sup>th</sup> Dec-2000 to 13<sup>th</sup> Jan-2001.</p><p><b>Affiliations/Memberships of Professional bodies</b><b>: </b></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Life Member of Institution of Engineers (INDIA) and Member of Society of&nbsp; Automotive Engineers (SAE) Membership No. 7007210009 <b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </b></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><b>Honors / Distinction / Recognition by International bodies</b><b>