(1, 'How to fill up a registration form?', 'The registration form has your photograph scanned on it.It also consists of information like your semester subjects and your address.You need to furnish the other details as per the instructions in the form.You need to attach the copy of fee receipt with the dean''s copy of the registration form.All the copies of the registration form should submitted to the faculty advisors of their respective departments.', 0),
(2, 'How to fill up examination form?', 'The examination form can be obtained from the academic section before some days (as notified by academic section)from the commencement of the examination.You need to furnish details like your semester subjects and your name, roll no. and other related details.It should be submitted to the academic section.', 0),
(3, 'How to change spelling mistake of name or any such error on the grade card or certificate?', 'You need to write an application to dean through faculty adviser giving the details of the mistakes.Further, you need to attach  copy of your original 10th class certificate/grade card/related certificate for verification.', 0),
(4, 'What to do in case of loss of grade card/identity card/any certificate?', 'You need to lodge an FIR in the nearest police station stating your loss.Then,you need to submit the copy of FIR along with the application and prescribed fee for new grade card/certificate to dean through faculty adviser.', 0),
(5, 'How to make online Fee payment through SBI?', '</br>Step 1:Click on the link <a href="https://www.onlinesbi.com/prelogin/icollecthome.htm" target="_blank" class="pagelink">www.onlinesbi.com/prelogin/icollecthome.htm</a>  for online fee payment </br>Step 2:This link will take you to the SBI window.</br>Step 3:Read the rules on the first page and tick that you have read all the rules and then,you need to click on proceed button.</br>Step 4:Then,choose jharkhand and then choose NIT jamshedpur.</br>Step 5: Furnish the details as per the instructions in the form.</br>Step 6:After that, make the fee payment through appropriate payment option.', 0),
(6, 'Instructions to invigilators during examination', '<a href="uploads/Instructions to invigilators during examination.pdf">Instructions to invigilators during examination </a>', 1),
(7, 'What are code of conduct for students during examination', '<a href="uploads/Code of conduct for students during examination.pdf">Download Code of conduct for students during examination.pdf</a>', 1);
